Class ListIteratorImpl<E>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.pepstock.charba.client.commons.IteratorImpl<E>
      • org.pepstock.charba.client.commons.ListIteratorImpl<E>
  • Type Parameters:
    E - type of list
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.util.Iterator<E>, java.util.ListIterator<E>

    public class ListIteratorImpl<E>
extends IteratorImpl<E>
implements java.util.ListIterator<E>
    An iterator for lists that allows the programmer to traverse the list in either direction, modify the list during iteration, and obtain the iterator's current position in the list.
    Author:
    Andrea "Stock" Stocchero
